    <string name="help_quick_start_html">
    &lt;b&gt;Via Quick Start&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    1. Tap the green play button on the main screen.&lt;br/&gt;
    2. Grant permission when prompted (only once).&lt;br/&gt;
    3. The button turns red and a popup says "Recording Started".&lt;br/&gt;
    4. Your journey is now being logged automatically.&lt;br/&gt;
    5. To stop, tap the red button again. It will turn green.
    </string>

    <string name="help_sensor_settings_html">
    &lt;b&gt;Via Sensor Settings&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
    1. Tap the profile icon > Sensor Settings.&lt;br/&gt;
    2. Toggle the sensors you want to use.&lt;br/&gt;
    3. Check the descriptions under each sensor to understand what it tracks.&lt;br/&gt;
    4. Tap "Start Recording" at the top.&lt;br/&gt;
    5. Grant permissions only for selected sensors.&lt;br/&gt;
    6. You may leave the page. It keeps recording.&lt;br/&gt;
    7. To stop, return and tap "Stop Recording".
    </string>


